    "Yahweh is telling you now, Zerubavel, to be strong. And be strong, highВҰ375935 priestВҰ375934 Yehoshua, andВҰ375922 be strong all you peopleВҰ375939 of the land. ArmyВҰ375951 commanderВҰ375951 Yahweh declares that I'm with you ",
